description: Join us on the latest food truck adventure… Southern Comfort Road Trip by Stover Bros Cafe!Stover Bros Cafe's food truck serves delicious comfort food featuring various mac n cheese creations, delicious sliders, sandwiches and more.Charles has traveled and explored a lot. And on those famous road trips he has tasted a lot of great food. Now he plans to share some of those great southern tastes with you.
name: Southern Comfort Road Trip
